{"tid":1849900,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"2名港人在廣東確診 有武漢旅行史或居住史","createTime":"2020-01-29T09:39:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T10:14:23.000Z","uid":212626,"like":8,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"03ecca1ff326693b897ed401d25921a6fba29d44","tid":1849900,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T09:39:42.000Z","msg":"廣東省政府新聞辦今日下午舉行例行新聞發佈會。廣東省衞健委黨組成員、副主任陳祝生表示，截至目前為止，該省發現的確診病人中，有3人是外籍（其中2人澳洲籍、1人巴基斯坦籍），有2人是香港人，這5人都有武漢旅行或居住史。<br />\n<br />\n陳祝生未有提到2名確診港人在省內何地，或其他詳細資料，只就巴基斯坦籍患者提供了細節。陳指，廣州發現的這一例巴基斯坦籍留學生，是在武漢一所大學讀書，1月21日到深圳，24日到廣州，26日出現症狀，就診後即被住院隔離，現已轉到指定醫院留醫，病情穩定。至於如何受感染，目前還不是很明朗，當局會做一些流行病學調查。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200129/AT6BWZZYSGAXRUMCPNP2NDODZE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200129%2FAT6BWZZYSGAXRUMCPNP2NDODZE%2F&d=5FuYkWQ3QtYmval6ncx7Jr32HZRMtn4xjJY4gFhUisg%3D&h=8aeffb31\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200129%2FAT6BWZZYSGAXRUMCPNP2NDODZE%2F&h=43f57d06\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200129/AT6BWZZYSGAXRUMCPNP2NDODZE/</a>"},{"pid":"8a5c7c32b6af41974d16d57391cc0b6fb5c412fa","tid":1849900,"uid":114097,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T09:43:20.000Z","msg":"武事嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24b511ff27e3635d894f534e57a3415e3670729d","tid":1849900,"uid":91432,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T09:44:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce096f2d3c47b9e4dbe632fc7efa56bd13758625","tid":1849900,"uid":108016,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T09:48:15.000Z","msg":"依啲先係愛國<br />\n而家仲留喺香港班藍屍唔該收收皮"},{"pid":"bee5f1874b474d88812bd541a901d97defaca789","tid":1849900,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T09:48:49.000Z","